{{TOCright}}

Nastavení pro [[Image:Workbench_Spreadsheet.svg|24px|link=Spreadsheet_Workbench]] [[Spreadsheet_Workbench/cs|Pracovní prostředí Spreadsheet]] najdete v [[Preferences Editor/cs|Editoru nastavení]]. V menu vyberte {{MenuCommand|Upravit→ Nastavení}} a poté {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Workbench_Spreadsheet.svg|16px]] Spreadsheet}}. Tato skupina je k dispozici pouze v případě, že byl v aktuální relaci FreeCADu Spreadsheet načten.

There is only one page: Spreadsheet.

[[Image:Preferences_Spreadsheet_Page_Spreadsheet.png]]

On this page you can specify the following:

{| class="wikitable"
!style="width: 33%;"|Name
!style="width: 66%;"|Description
|-
| {{MenuCommand|Delimiter character}}
|  The character used as field delimiter.
|-
| {{MenuCommand|Quote character}}
|  The character used to delimit strings.
|-
| {{MenuCommand|Escape character}}
|  The character used to prevent the following character from being parsed.
|-
| {{MenuCommand|Default zoom level}}
| The default zoom level for spreadsheets (from 60% to 160%). {{Version|1.1}}
|-
| {{MenuCommand|Show alias in cell with format}}
|  If checked, and if the cell has a value and an alias, the alias and value are shown in the given format. {{Value|%V}} is the placeholder for the value and {{Value|%A}} the placeholder for the alias. {{Version|1.0}}
|}


